    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Actually, before you finalize that, I need a quick risk assessment. How much is this shift toward underserved areas going to impact our overall infrastructure stability and the company's bottom line? I need to be able to explain to the board why our projected maintenance costs are going up and our asset lifespan in the high-value districts might decrease.",
